This project's engine/ check logic was built by referencing and, in several files, closely
porting code from Auriti-Labs/geo-optimizer-skill (MIT license, Copyright (c) 2026
Juan Camilo Auriti — https://github.com/Auriti-Labs/geo-optimizer-skill). See
THIRD_PARTY_LICENSES/geo-optimizer-skill-LICENSE for the full upstream license text.

Close ports (logic, thresholds, and control flow ported near-verbatim, rewritten as our own
module layout with no composite score and an added `n/a` status):

- engine/checks/robots.py       - RFC 9309 parser and bot classification, from
                                   utils/robots_parser.py and core/audit_robots.py
- engine/checks/llms_txt.py     - from core/audit_llms.py
- engine/checks/schema.py       - JSON-LD extraction/validation, from core/audit_schema.py
- engine/checks/meta.py         - from core/audit_meta.py
- engine/checks/content.py      - content-quality logic (question-shaped-heading detection is
                                   NEW, not in the upstream), from core/audit_content.py
- engine/checks/signals.py      - from core/audit_signals.py
- engine/checks/ai_discovery.py - from core/audit_ai_discovery.py
- engine/checks/negative_signals.py - from core/audit_negative.py
- engine/checks/brand_entity.py - from core/audit_brand.py
- engine/checks/injection.py    - all 8 cloaking/prompt-injection detection categories, from
                                   core/injection_detector.py
- engine/shared.py              - trimmed AI_BOTS/CITATION_BOTS registry and threshold
                                   constants, from models/config.py; flatten_graph() and
                                   normalize_brand_name() from core/audit_brand.py

Original to this project (no upstream equivalent):
- engine/http_client.py    - fetch layer with timeout/retry/size-cap/URL-scheme hardening
- engine/orchestrator.py   - two-input-mode (URL / local-file) sequencing
- engine/cli.py            - entrypoint, --self-test
- engine/models.py         - no-score, 4-value-status (pass/partial/fail/n/a) result shape
- The question-shaped-heading check inside engine/checks/content.py
- agents/GeoAgent.md
- install.sh

Deliberately NOT ported (see GEO-Agent-Plan.md and the approved build plan for the full list):
composite scoring, the CheckRegistry plugin system, the async httpx twin, citability.py,
trust_stack.py, sentiment/monitor/history/snapshots/drift/competitive-narrative/
hallucination-bait, CI formatters, the web frontend, Docker, audit_cdn.py, audit_js.py.
